Definition: the federal government's program to locate and investigate and clean up the worst uncontrolled and abandoned toxic waste sites nationwide
Example: administered by the Environmental Protection Agency; some have intimated that the Superfund's money may have turned into a political slush fund
Synonyms: Superfund, program, the, federal, government, s, to, locate, and, investigate, clean, up, worst, uncontrolled, abandoned, toxic, waste, sites, nationwide, administered, by, Environmental, Protection, Agency, some, have, intimated, that, money, may, turned, into, a, political, slush, fund
Category: noun.cognition
